_aChangeLog.text: - Changed layout of the A bombsite
- Changed layout of the B bombsite
Fixed CT and T spawn points

_aLatestUpdates._sText: Thank you to w6a7z99 for playing my map and giving me feedback! It means a lot and gives me the motivation to pursue and improve my mapping skills. Most of the issues they have addressed have been fixed and improved on.

_sText: Recently came back to mapping for fun, created this within a day thought it might be fun to play with friends. Hopefully whoever downloads this will enjoy it! I'll try to update it if there is demand because there is some stuff I'm not too happy about in this map.
